@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### chat session 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "테스트 세션",
  "system_message": "You are a helpful assistant."
}

### chat session 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/

### chat session 단건 조회 (id 바꿔서 테스트)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/1

### chat session 제목 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/1/title
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수정된 세션 제목"
}

### chat session 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/1